			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4464906">
									

<p>This does an excellent job conveying a metric ton of exposition without being boring. Penelope and Wren are entertaining characters that feel grounded in a contemporary fiction setting, and the incorporation of the Salt and Pepper Diner skit into the narrative is perfectly tuned for a Gamers Against Weed story without inducing eye-rolls. I look forward to the continuing adventures of Steak and Book.</p>

							</div>

								
					
