			<div class="content" id="post-content-4465408">
									

<p>Thank you kindly! I love writing these characters &#8212; they've become much more distinct in my mind since the one-off jokes of SCP-4581. I'm glad the central gimmick comes across well, too; I feel like simple referentialism is too easy, so I try to make it a transformative thing. Looking forward to sharing more!</p>

