<p>Of all the stories in this series, this has got to be my favorite. In addition to A Random Day's comments, I would also like to add that this story was amazingly understandable. While I don't have a very firm grasp on a lot of the concepts presented in this piece, the language and framing (plus context) made sure that I was possessed with the ghosts of those concepts for at least the duration of the story. Special props to how you dealt with pataphysics.</p>
